    <section id="about">

       

        <div class="container-fluid" id="color">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-12 wow fadeIn">
                   
                    <h1>Decision Fatigue</h1>
                    <p>A real psychological condition in which a person’s productivity suffers as a result of becoming mentally exhausted from making so many irrelevant decisions.</p>
                    <hr class="colored">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row text-center content-row">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        
                        <h3>Reduce Decision Fatigue</h3>
                        <p>Discover why a number of very successful people have adopted this philosophy in their daily routines. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        
                        <h3>Easy to Look Great</h3>
                        <p>Armoire is built to recommend customized outfits based on your life. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".6s">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        
                        <h3>Life is complicated enough</h3>
                        <p> After using Armoire, one might find that they are significantly less stressed, more productive and more fulfilled.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay=".8s">
                    <div class="about-content">
                        
                        <h3>Feedback from friends and family</h3>
                        <p>Friends, family and stylists can connect and comment on your outfits. Follow trendsetters and gain inspiration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div><!-- end of row -->
    </section>


    <aside class="cta-quote" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path("fashion/bg-aside.jpg")%>')">
        <div class="container wow fadeIn">
           <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <span class="quote">‘You’ll see I wear only gray or <span class="text-primary">blue</span> suits. I’m trying to pare down decisions. I don’t want to make decisions about what I’m eating or wearing. Because I have too many other decisions to make.’</span>
                    <hr class=" colored">
                    <a class="btn btn-primary-li page-scroll" href="#collection" id="barack">-President Barack Obama</a>
                </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </aside>

        <section id="process" class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-lg-12 wow fadeIn">
